                </p>
            </div>
            <div class"col-sm-12">
                <h3>Saturday, October 1</h3>
                <center><img src="/img/food-1.png"></center>
                <p>
                    Reception
                    Dinner will be served!
                    Afterwards, a little music, dancing, and dessert!
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class"col-sm-12">
                <h3>Saturday, October 1</h3>
                <center><img src="/img/transport.png"></center>
                <p>
                    Send Off
                    Time: 9:30 pm
                    Newlyweds are off!
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class"col-sm-12">
                <h3>Saturday, October 1</h3>
                <center><img src="/img/party.png"></center>
                <p>
                    After-Party
